Privacy Policy for Puchkaar

Last updated: 30/10/2023

Effective date: 30/10/2023

Thank you for choosing to use Puchkaar ("App"). At Puchkaar, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our App. By using Puchkaar, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

Puchkaar does not collect any personal information from users beyond basic login and sign-in details, such as your email address and password.

2. How We Use Your Information

We do not use the limited information collected for any purposes other than facilitating your access to the App and ensuring its functionality. Your email address is used for account verification and password recovery purposes.

3. Information Security

We take the security of your personal information seriously. We have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

4. Data Sharing

Puchkaar does not share your personal information with any third parties. We do not sell or rent your data.

5. Children's Privacy

Puchkaar is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If you believe that we may have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately at [Insert Contact Information], and we will promptly remove such data.

6. Changes to Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the revised Privacy Policy will be effective immediately upon posting. We recommend checking this page periodically for any updates.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at [Insert Contact Information].

8. Consent

By using Puchkaar, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

